  "notes": [
    "This configuration resolves City of Mesa base zoning by coordinate.",
    "The configured source is the public zoning feature layer published through the official City of Mesa Open GIS portal.",
    "Description contains the published zoning code and district name; for example, LC - Limited Commercial.",
    "Previous_Zoning, RelatedCase, Ordinance, and Link are retained when published and may provide useful zoning-history context.",
    "Mesa publishes zoning overlays separately; this base-zoning lookup does not determine whether an overlay, planned-area standard, form-based-code condition, or other supplemental regulation applies.",
